text.tspan: A Really Short Update To The Journal
Written by Cassidy James. Published December 20th, 2011

flowRoot.flowPara: After reading the Journal, are you left wanting more? Check us out on your favorite social networks for even more news, updates, and commentary.

We push our Journal entries out to our Facebook page, so it's a great way to keep up with everything. Plus we'll often post polls and random comments to interact with our users. If you like elementary, be sure to "Like" us on Facebook!
Looking for that quick, short-form interaction with elementary? Hit us up on Twitter to follow bits of news, info, and design thoughts.
